quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  58,14,"Ntubabona bamwe bagize ubucuti hamwe n’abantu bashavuriwe n’Imana, abo ntibari kumwe namwe, kandi ntibari kumwe nabo, kandi barahira k’ububeshi mugihe bazi y’uko ari ababeshi"
  58,15,"Imana yaraba teguriye ibihano bikaze cane, mu vy’ukuri muvyo bahora bagira n’ibintu bibi cane"
  58,16,"Bagize indahiro zabo kuba arizo nkinzo zabo n’ukuzitira inzira yagenywe n’Imana, rero kuribo hazoba ibihano biba mara maza"
  58,17,"Amatungo yabo hamwe n’ibibondo vyabo ntaco bizoba marira n’ikintu na kimwe imbere y’Imana, abo nibo bantu bo mu muriro udahera, muriwo bazo wuba mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose"
  58,18,"Umusi Imana izozura abantu bose hanyuma barahire nkuko barahira iwanyu, bazo kwikeka yuko baronse ikintu c’ububeshi, mu vy’ukuri abo nibo babeshi nyakuri"
  58,19,"Shetani yarabicariye mukubibagiza kwibuka Imana yabo y’ukuri, uwo niwo murwi wa Shetani, kandi ni mutegere neza mu vy’ukuri umurwi wa Shetani niwo ufise uruhombo"
  58,20,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo abo ni muri bamwe bazoteterwa
  58,21,"Imana iramaze kwandika, yuko atankeka jewe nzotsinda hamwe n’intumwa zanje zose, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi n’intsinzi ihagije"
  58,22,"Nturonka abantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka yuko baba kunda bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, naho boba ari abavyeyi babo, canke ibibondo vyabo, canke bene wabo, canke incuti zabo, abo nibo banditswe mu mitima yabo n’ukwemera kwabo n’ukubashiramwo ubushobozi k’umutima uvuye iwe, kandi izobinjiza mu mirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yabo, iyo niyo bazobayo mu buzima bwabo bwose, n’Imana yarabemereye kuribo, nabo barayemereye"